      "note": "Resolved 4 open cross-domain decisions in decisions.md: (1) DB topology = one shared SQLite file with registry_/tool_/provider_/policy_ prefixes, one handle, no ATTACH, no cross-package FK (DAG-neutral baseline that agent-compiler already assumes); (2) context-condition eval = ALL matching included with deterministic total order (position, version, slug), is_required unmatched => error; (3) keep both context_condition + context_rules with a single shared predicate evaluator + additive union (junction wins dedup); (4) version pin is per-reference (slug, version_pin?), null=latest-at-resolve, identical at junction/policy/experiment sites. Architecture guard passes 3/3 (exit 0). No decision changes the DAG."
